author: Benjamin Fearnow
title: Coronavirus Task Force's Dr. Deborah Birx Says COVID-19 Likely Moved From Animal to Human, Originated in China
description: "It's going to take us a while to really map and trace this particular virus, map it through its experience in humans, and get the scientific evidence of where this virus originated."
